    title: 'Exploring Packaging in Colonial America',
    type: 'ARTICLE',
    subhead:
      'In this blog, we celebrate the 4th of July by discussing how packaging was used in the American colonies. We focus on barrels and glass bottles, talking about the use, materials, and fun facts related to the use of these packaging systems in the colonies. ',
