    title: 'Top FREE AI Tools for Packaging Design',
    type: 'ARTICLE',
    subhead:
      'In this blog we will explore the top free AI platforms/tools to help with packaging design inspiration and workflow. We explore Fotor AI, Canva Magic Studio, Adobe Express, and Pixlr—covering how the use the platforms, and testing them with a uniform packaging related prompt—sustainable cereal packaging.',
