      '<p><span style="color: rgb(13, 13, 13)">How was COVID-19 affecting packaging and the supply chain in the early days of the pandemic? It certainly affected us all and changed the way we live, if only for a specific amount of time. The pandemic impacted the way we purchase goods and receive them because of the disruption to the supply chain. In this episode, we talk with Claire Krause, Packaging Consultant with TricoBraun. Claire discusses the strain the packaging industry felt in order to meet the global demand for cleaning and sanitizing supplies.</span></p>',
