      'When you see a package on the store shelf, do you see the front or the back of the package first? Now, you may be wondering if this is a trick question—of course you see the front of the package first! (Unless someone has put it back in its place improperly.) But the nutritional labeling is not on the front, and that may be the most critical information a consumer needs to be concerned with when buying a food product. ',
