    content:
      '<p><span style="color: rgb(23, 23, 23)">Our Founder, </span><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/drandrewhurley/">Dr. Andrew Hurley</a><span style="color: rgb(23, 23, 23)">, wrote for </span><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.packworld.com/home/article/21142166/ecomm-package-storytelling">Packaging World</a><span style="color: rgb(23, 23, 23)"> in an article titled, "E-Comm Package Storytelling," speaking on the power of effective eCommerce packaging in terms of branding and storytelling.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 23, 23)"><strong>Dr. Hurley stated</strong>:</span></p><blockquote><p>Unlike retail packaging, which benefits from consistent messaging and branding, eCommerce packages are first viewed after purchase. Each delivery could provide a new insight or character of the brand.</p></blockquote><p>Read the full publication here: <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.packworld.com/home/article/21142166/ecomm-package-storytelling">https://www.packworld.com/home/article/21142166/ecomm-package-storytelling</a>.</p><h3 class="font-bold" style="text-align: start"><strong>LEARN MORE ABOUT PACKAGING DESIGN</strong></h3><p style="text-align: start">Here at the Packaging School, we have a collection of online packaging design courses designed <em>by</em> packaging professionals <em>for</em> packaging professionals!</p><p style="text-align: start"><strong>Our suite of packaging design courses include:</strong></p><ul><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/packaging-design-workflow">Packaging Design Workflow</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/leveraging-human-factors-in-packaging-design">Leveraging Human Factors in Packaging Design</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/introduction-to-corrugated-design">Intro to Corrugated Design</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/package-printing">Package Printing</a></p></li></ul><p style="text-align: start">We also have a collection of packaging design videos on our <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/@Packagingschool">YouTube</a> channel, including our most popular video to date—<a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://youtu.be/euacI5VTBhY?si=vidPR70DR5tIS6my">How Package Design Affects Sales</a>.</p>',
