      '<p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/drandrewhurley/">Dr. Andrew Hurley</a>, our Founder and a Professor of Packaging Science at Clemson University, recently wrote for <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.upmraflatac.com/news-and-stories/blog/2019/11/6-tips-for-convincing-label-and-package-design/">UPM Raflatac\'s blog</a>, discussing 6 tips for effective label and package design.</p><h3 class="font-bold">Dr. Andrew Hurley\'s 6 Tips</h3><blockquote><ol><li><p>Use information (including colors) sparingly</p></li><li><p>A picture is worth a thousand words</p></li><li><p>Minimize fonts and lines of text</p></li><li><p>Don\'t put everything on the front panel</p></li><li><p>Don\'t forget the power of word-of-mouth</p></li><li><p>Don\'t launch without extensive testing</p></li></ol></blockquote><p>Read the full article here: <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.upmraflatac.com/news-and-stories/blog/2019/11/6-tips-for-convincing-label-and-package-design/">https://www.upmraflatac.com/news-and-stories/blog/2019/11/6-tips-for-convincing-label-and-package-design/</a>.</p><h3 class="font-bold" style="text-align: start"><strong>Learn More About Packaging Design</strong></h3><p style="text-align: start">Here at the Packaging School, we have a collection of online packaging design courses designed <em>by</em> packaging professionals <em>for</em> packaging professionals!</p><p style="text-align: start"><strong>Our suite of packaging design courses include:</strong></p><ul><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/packaging-design-workflow">Packaging Design Workflow</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/leveraging-human-factors-in-packaging-design">Leveraging Human Factors in Packaging Design</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/introduction-to-corrugated-design">Intro to Corrugated Design</a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://packagingschool.com/courses/package-printing">Package Printing</a></p></li></ul><p style="text-align: start">We also have a collection of packaging design videos on our <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/@Packagingschool">YouTube</a> channel, including our most popular video to date—<a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://youtu.be/euacI5VTBhY?si=vidPR70DR5tIS6my">How Package Design Affects Sales</a>.</p>',
